{"tid":1587104,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【粵譯】《忍者上網懶人包》","createTime":"2019-09-22T09:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T09:22:09.000Z","uid":69753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6d57ade887e1f42bc69adf2b4342a1f5c9f00c89","tid":1587104,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:19:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">原文：<a href=\"https://digdeeper.neocities.org/ghost/ninja.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigdeeper.neocities.org%2Fghost%2Fninja.html&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=a394918a\" target=\"_blank\">https://digdeeper.neocities.org/ghost/ninja.html</a><br />\nNinja's guide to the Internet<br />\nby Dig Deeper</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">序言</span></span></div><br />\n喺呢一刻，可能有數以百計嘅<em>「網絡私隱懶人包」</em>，但絕大部份都係呃鬼食豆腐。佢哋推介邪惡公司嘅瀏覽器（例如<ins>Firefox</ins><em> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">*1</span></em>）；<ins>偷資料</ins><em> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">*2</span></em>嘅電郵供應商（例如Mailfence、Runbox）；<ins>懸疣附贅</ins><em> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">*3</span></em>嘅addons（例如Privacy Badger、NoScript）；需要電話號碼嘅通訊軟件（例如Signal、Telegram）；用心不良嘅VPNs（例如Proton）；佢哋太注重軟件伺服器喺邊，而忽視政策同功能；墮入失實宣傳嘅陷阱；收「贊助費」去推介軟件；對好嘅軟件視而不見，亦無心提醒你要做啲咩。<br />\n我務求避免以上嘅問題，整一個<em><strong>究極懶人包</strong></em>。而最正嘅係，<em><strong>所有嘢都唔使錢</strong></em>！<br />\n吓？你問點解叫做「忍者上網懶人包」？因為佢哋<ins>潛行如影</ins> <em><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">*4</span></em>。而且，你唔覺得個名好撚型咩？<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">*1：<a href=\"https://digdeeper.neocities.org/ghost/mozilla.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigdeeper.neocities.org%2Fghost%2Fmozilla.html&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=2ca1404b\" target=\"_blank\">https://digdeeper.neocities.org/ghost/mozilla.html</a><br />\n*2：<a href=\"https://digdeeper.neocities.org/ghost/email.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigdeeper.neocities.org%2Fghost%2Femail.html&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=f584cc87\" target=\"_blank\">https://digdeeper.neocities.org/ghost/email.html</a><br />\n*3：<a href=\"https://digdeeper.neocities.org/ghost/addons.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigdeeper.neocities.org%2Fghost%2Faddons.html&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=0ac8f3f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://digdeeper.neocities.org/ghost/addons.html</a><br />\n*4：<a href=\"http://www.ninjaencyclopedia.com/techniques/hide.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ninjaencyclopedia.com%2Ftechniques%2Fhide.html&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=de65808b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ninjaencyclopedia.com/techniques/hide.html</a></span></em>"},{"pid":"0e41701f57dd0625361782b0cd52eadd81b1c74b","tid":1587104,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:20:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">電腦系統</span></span></div><br />\n首先要講嘅，必然係電腦系統，話晒你所有軟件都喺佢上面運行。不言而喻，咪用Windows － 佢<ins>監視著你嘅一舉一動</ins> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>*1</em></span>，又有<strong><em>熄唔到嘅自動更新</em></strong>。雖然新版本畀你取消部份監視功能，但其實無補於事。就算你取消晒，Windows照<ins>瞞住你每分鐘send十一個請求</ins> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>*2</em></span>。<br />\n而Linux都有佢嘅瑕疵，Ubuntu曾經有過<ins>私隱問題</ins> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>*3</em></span>，而systemd可以話係大公司<ins>操控Linux嘅工具</ins> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>*4</em></span>。最好嘅方法係用冇systemd嘅Linux系統，例如<ins>Salix</ins> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>*5</em></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>*1：<a href=\"http://www.leighb.com/win10.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.leighb.com%2Fwin10.htm&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=3eb2e65f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.leighb.com/win10.htm</a><br />\n*2：<a href=\"https://thehackernews.com/2016/02/microsoft-windows10-privacy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthehackernews.com%2F2016%2F02%2Fmicrosoft-windows10-privacy.html&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=ec439ea5\" target=\"_blank\">https://thehackernews.com/2016/02/microsoft-windows10-privacy.html</a><br />\n*3：<a href=\"https://www.gnu.org/philosophy/ubuntu-spyware.en.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gnu.org%2Fphilosophy%2Fubuntu-spyware.en.html&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=256d28dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gnu.org/philosophy/ubuntu-spyware.en.html</a><br />\n*4：<a href=\"http://www.softpanorama.org/Commercial_linuxes/Startup_and_shutdown/systemd.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.softpanorama.org%2FCommercial_linuxes%2FStartup_and_shutdown%2Fsystemd.shtml&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=b02ce14d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.softpanorama.org/Commercial_linuxes/Startup_and_shutdown/systemd.shtml</a><br />\n*5：<a href=\"https://digdeeper.neocities.org/ghost/salix.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigdeeper.neocities.org%2Fghost%2Fsalix.html&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=db692221\" target=\"_blank\">https://digdeeper.neocities.org/ghost/salix.html</a></em></span><br />\n<br />\n譯者補充：用OpenBSD／Gentoo／Salix當然最好最安全，不過其實Debian／Arch／Mint已經夠。當然，你正常人要返工做功課打機都係用返Windows／MacOS喇。"},{"pid":"d19b500676eb16c2e2ca0dc237c0b3427b3eeaa5","tid":1587104,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}